message:
Add LICENSE.

Cover code under MIT License and update README.md.
Add Travis CI badge to README.md

Update build status badge to reflect GitHub workflow.

The tests are now run via a GitHub workflow instead of Travis.

Use common collection of format tests.

This allows us to use the same set of tests across all the data
respositories.  Note that the tests from openelections-format-tests
don't check for required column headers yet so that test has been
omitted.
Add badge to indicate status of data tests.
